    "description": "回家的路上，你把车停在最近的便利店加油，然后很快意识到关于这个地方的谣言是真的。在这款 PS1 风格的生存恐怖游戏中，生存下来并逃离 Oldlake Stalker！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 短篇恐怖游戏<br></li><li> 低多边形 PS1 风格<br></li><li> 没有随机惊吓<br></li><li> 多个结局<br></li><li> 几个隐藏的秘密</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/062443f5085c90850f4f5b88706553dd.webp?t=1734575255\" width=627 height=52 /></span><br><br><strong>解谜</strong><br>以密室逃脱的方式，玩家将解开谜题以逃离他们被锁在的便利店地下室。在解谜时，请确保房间中的所有物品都和你醒来时一样，否则绑匪会注意到并攻击你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/15ebe761270768ea5a5da93c5e617a77.poster.avif?t=1734575255\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/15ebe761270768ea5a5da93c5e617a77.webm?t=1734575255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/15ebe761270768ea5a5da93c5e617a77.mp4?t=1734575255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/b30fd4c53de7e199d458a3d2b414a847.webp?t=1734575255\" width=627 height=52 /></span><br><br><strong>生存</strong><br>玩家还需要做出决定并在被追赶时生存下来。游戏中有几件物品可以帮助你逃脱，所以一定要仔细查看，这可能会救你的命。游戏有多个结局，所以每个人都会有不同的体验，让游戏非常具有可玩性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/86e32dff6940699233cd31ba6845c012.poster.avif?t=1734575255\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/86e32dff6940699233cd31ba6845c012.webm?t=1734575255\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/86e32dff6940699233cd31ba6845c012.mp4?t=1734575255\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143010/extras/8f75579431c1a5e0cc57a52f1b772890.webp?t=1734575255\" width=627 height=52 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2>你正在穿越 Oldlake 县。很多人都告诉你要远离这个地方，因为该地区发生过无数起失踪事件。回家的路上，你把车停在最近的便利店加油，很快意识到关于这个地方的谣言是真的。在这款 PS1 风格的恐怖游戏中生存下来并逃离 Oldlake Stalker！<br><br>LunaApps 制作的第一款恐怖游戏，具有互动环境和令人毛骨悚然的角色，同时你可以在密室逃脱谜题中生存下来并探索便利店。",
